[Start]  
   ↓  
[User Sends a Message]  
   ↓  
[Preprocessing]  
   ↓  
[Intent Matching]  
   ↓  
[Decision: Is intent found?]  
   ├── Yes → [Response Handling (Intent Found)] → [Display Response on UI] → [Decision: Is the conversation over?]  
   │        ├── Yes → [End]  
   │        └── No → Loop back to [User Sends a Message]  
   └── No → [Response Handling (Fallback)] → [Display Response on UI] → [Decision: Is the conversation over?]  
            ├── Yes → [End]  
            └── No → Loop back to [User Sends a Message]
